        </mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class='text-size color-black'  padding-top='25px'>
        <p style='color:#6366F1;font-weight:bold;font-size:12px;line-height:0;'>STEP 3</p>
        <p style='font-weight:900;line-height:1;'>Leave a comment</p>
        <p style='color:#9CA3AF;font-size:14px;line-height:1.2;'>Explain how the third step of the giveaway is working.</p>
        <a href='#' style='font-size:14px;line-height:1;'>Share now &rarr;</a>
        </mj-text>
